title: The Fountains in the Park is pet friendly come check us out.

posting_body: ['We have a great one bedroom apartment for August.', '\xa0 We are pet friendly , come take a tour of our property and feel free to bring your four leged friend to.', 'The Fountains in the Park Apartments is nestled away in a beautiful setting with walking trails, yet conveniently close to the Twin Cities.', 'Fountains in the Park Apartments is located in the central neighborhood of Brooklyn Park, MN with easy access to I-94 and I-694.', '-Walk-in Closets', '-Private Stall Garage w/remote', '-Balcony/Patio', '-Dishwasher', '-Gas Range', '-Vanity Area', '-On-Site Maintenance', '-Split Bathroom', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-On-Site Management', '-Washer and Dryer in Unit', '-Off', 'Street Parking', 'Call:', 'show contact info', '5700 73rd Avenue North, Brooklyn Park, MN 55429', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
